    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The shaman can touch a willing ally and cause its skin to thicken and sprout thick, shaggy fur. The creature gains a +2 enhancement bonus to natural armor and cold resistance 5 for 10 minutes.</p>\n<p>At 9th level, the enhancement bonus increases to +3 and the cold resistance to 10.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, this enhancement bonus increases to +4 and the cold resistance to 15.</p>\n<p>The shaman can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + her Charisma bonus.</p>",
